post_text:
**IMPORTANT UPDATE** for Monday, April 27th, covering:

- Missing or Incomplete Grades (turn in to teacher(s) by May 15th to avoid conversion to a failing grade(s));

- Skyward Video for Parents showing how to view student grades and also how to sign up for email notifications when grades are recorded, based on your own settings/preferences;

- Progress Reports for 6th Nine Weeks and every Friday going forward, posted in Skyward;

- Tech Support via online form or (new) phone number; and a reminder for how to contact your child's teacher, or any other G-PISD administrator who can offer support you may need at home.

To review this important information, visit www.g-pisd.org/update

Thank you, G-PISD Administration

